      • changeResponseTime

        protected boolean changeResponseTime(Tenant tenant,
                                     long avgResponseTime)
        Changes the average response time of the method MRubisNames.getPersonalizedItems_Signature of the interface MRubisNames.browseRegionService_InterfaceType_FqName provided by exactly one component of the given tenant. Thus, the corresponding PerformanceStats element is updated by setting new values to its attributes such that the average response time is avgResponseTime.
        Parameters:
        target - the give tenant
        avgResponseTime - the average response time to be set
        Returns:
        true if the average response could be successfully updated, otherwisefalse.
